                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.15">
                                <locus from="149rb" to="152va"/>
                                <title type="incomplete">Salām-hymns for Ḫǝdār</title>
                                <note>The collection ends with salām-hymns to Anne, the mother of Mary; Minas; 
                                    Archelaos, the martyr<!-- I did not find any person with the name "Archelaos, the martyr" -->; 
                                    ʾElsāʿ, the abbot<!-- I did not find any person with the name ʾElsāʿ the abbot --> 
                                    and to <persName ref="PRS7696Pachomiu">Pachomius</persName>. The text ends abruptly.</note>
                                <explicit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለኪ፡ ለጸሎተ፡ ጻድቃን፡ ምዕራጋ። ከመ፡ አስካለ፡ ወይን፡ ዲበ፡ ሐረጋ። <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ሰላም፡ ለከ፡
                                    ፈጻሜ፡ ሕማማት፡ በሐሰሳ። ዐቢየ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ሚናስ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ሰላም፡ ለክሙ፡ ለአርከለዎስ፡ ሰማዕት፡ ወኤልሳዕ፡ አበ፡ ምኔት። ወምስለ፡
                                    እሉ፡ <choice resp="PRS8999Strelcyn"><sic>ጳአኵሚስ፡</sic><corr>ጳኵሚስ፡</corr></choice> ኅቡረ፡ ሥርዓት። 
                                    <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ዘአቅረብከ፡ በማኅሌት፡ አዘኪርየ፡ አእላፈ። እለ፡ ተጸምዱከ፡ ዘልፈ። ለለ፡ ይትነበብ፡ ተወከፍ፡ ዘንዴትየ፡ መጽሐፈ። 
                                    እን<gap reason="lost"/></explicit> 
                            </msItem>
